{"tid":1678628,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角食肆被催淚彈射中 職員疑幫克警補鑊：唔關警察事","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T17:55:20.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9b24f85fec97eb9298f7e975de2dc1becc04f6","tid":1678628,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191027/large/1572189631_0dea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191027%2Flarge%2F1572189631_0dea.jpg&h=0dddd2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防到場調查。文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191027/large/1572189631_a1f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191027%2Flarge%2F1572189631_a1f1.jpg&h=877b522d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n職員在催淚彈殼上灑上白米，疑似意圖掩飾證據。江子堯攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191027/large/1572189631_8738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191027%2Flarge%2F1572189631_8738.jpg&h=ae1cded9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後章記香港仔魚蛋王拉上鐵閘關門。文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n入夜後警方在旺角及尖沙嘴一帶施放多枚催淚彈，驅散市民，其間有防暴警在旺角中心對出的一段西洋菜南街推進，並在未有舉旗的情況下亂射催淚彈，其中一粒催淚彈更射入章記香港仔魚蛋王內，催淚彈卡在招牌後方，不斷冒出陣陣白煙。<br />\n<br />\n據知，職員一度試圖用水淋熄催淚彈，但不成功，食客見狀爭相走避，現場一片混亂，最後數名急救員合力搬開招牌，才能用水將催淚彈淋熄。事後整間舖頭烏燈黑火，消息指有市民向職員了解時，對方竟指「唔關警察事，係職員做嘅」，又在催淚彈殼上灑上白米，懷疑想掩飾克警的惡行。<br />\n<br />\n根據網民製作的「黃藍商戶清單地圖」網站顯示，章記香港仔魚蛋王為「親共商戶」，曾有網民表示：「一入到去就聽到佢哋喪鬧示威者，話佢哋咁做抵俾人打，都唔知立咩心腸去示威」，要求大家罷食。"},{"pid":"c1ee8aa7342b94439b937d3c2de5c38ee3e4ba6e","tid":1678628,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191027/60202054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60202054&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4eojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=071b6f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60202054&h=2c6b3302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191027/60202054</a>"},{"pid":"678d97f488b1901664a2889678e6ce1b34bb8457","tid":1678628,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"職員放催淚彈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}